==全球变暖的预期效果==
1993年至2003年，南极冰盖与格陵兰冰盖每年减少的冰，导致了海平面上升0.21 ± 0.35与0.21 ± 0.07 mm/year<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ipcc.ch/pdf/assessment-report/ar4/wg1/ar4-wg1-spm.pdf |title=Richard B. Alley et al.:''Summary for Policymakers'', A report of Working Group I of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change |accessdate=2012-09-17 |archive-date=2017-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171220143410/http://www.ipcc.ch/pdf/assessment-report/ar4/wg1/ar4-wg1-spm.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

